This chapter provides calendar-related subcommands for Canvas LMS.
The calendar commands allow users to list, view, and create calendar events.

Canvas provides several calendar-related API endpoints:
\begin{itemize}
\item [[get_calendar_events]] to list calendar events
\item [[get_calendar_event]] to get a specific calendar event
\item [[create_calendar_event]] to create new calendar events
\item [[get_upcoming_events]] to get upcoming events
\end{itemize}

